-- 02-04 Task 1: Biostimulator Product Dossiers — Sculptra Aesthetic
-- Product in manifest: Sculptra Aesthetic (2ce7a3d2)
-- Note: Radiesse is NOT in compile_manifest.json for plan 02-04; Sculptra is the only biostimulator entry.
-- Biostimulators category doc IDs (from 02-02 SUMMARY):
